323
00:16:04,590 --> 00:16:05,590
Your Excellency.

324
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:07,910
Please.

325
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:11,790
In my opinion,

326
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:14,080
Fan Xian is going to take over Neiku.

327
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,710
They took an account book back

328
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,520
