329
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:20,440
He won't give up on Yan Bingyun.

330
00:16:20,550 --> 00:16:22,400
Don't worry. It's like searching for a needle in a haystack.

331
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,590
We'd better be careful, just in case.

332
00:16:25,230 --> 00:16:26,550
Your Excellency, you can trust me.

333
00:16:26,710 --> 00:16:28,150
I've increased secret sentries.

334
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:36,520
Fan Xian reminded me of something today.

335
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,230
He has superb martial arts skill.

336
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,520
We need a Ninth Dan martial arts master

337
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:43,030
to keep an eye on him.

338
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,350
There is no Ninth Dan martial arts master

339
00:16:46,350 --> 00:16:48,030
available in the Embroidered Uniform Guards.

340
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:53,280
It's okay. We can borrow one.

341
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,200
Huh?

342
00:16:57,590 --> 00:16:58,440
There he is.

343
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,560
Mr. He.

344
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:10,310
Mr. He,

