349
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,800
Fan Xian from Nanqing.

350
00:17:19,350 --> 00:17:21,000
You asked me to keep an eye on Fan Xian?

351
00:17:21,230 --> 00:17:23,110
I know you're overqualified,

352
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:26,160
but you're the most suitable person.

353
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,000
Shen Zhong is right.

354
00:17:35,710 --> 00:17:37,280
You're the most suitable person.

355
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,280
You're lucky.

356
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:41,230
It's not about luck.

357
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,680
