359
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,160
There are so many Ninth Dan martial arts masters in Shangjing.

360
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,470
How did you know he'd come to me?

361
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:53,190
There are few

