00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:08,430
Of course he'd turn to you.

371
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,640
Did you get the account book so easily?

372
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:16,710
Yes, Your Excellency.

373
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:18,470
Without any twists and turns.

374
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:22,880
