395
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:01,310
What do you mean?

396
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:03,310
The Embroidered Uniform Guards

397
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:04,070
can empty a house,

398
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:05,070
but they can't kill

399
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:06,310
all residents in the street.

400
00:19:06,430 --> 00:19:07,590
I drank tea with some local people

401
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:08,350
and chatted with them

402
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:09,680
near that house today.

403
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:15,400
Sir, why are you sighing in despair?

404
00:19:16,230 --> 00:19:17,710
I came here for my relative,

405
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:19,190
but I was driven out.

406
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:20,160
Really?

407
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,350
Men's feelings are changeable.

408
00:19:22,350 --> 00:19:23,430
What will you do next?

409
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:24,680
I don't know.

410
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:26,520
I have to rent a house

411
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:27,430
and settle down.

412
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,880
I'm going to turn to a broker.

413
00:19:29,230 --> 00:19:30,190
You're lucky.

414
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:33,040
It happens that house is available.

415
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,710
Has it always been vacant?

416
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:36,710
Nah. Someone once lived there.

417
00:19:37,190 --> 00:19:38,470
Something happened to him.

418
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:39,760
Who lived there?

419
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:40,710
What happened?

420
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:41,880
A young man lived there.

421
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:42,800
He associated with

422
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:43,920
