423
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,040
or the rich.

424
00:19:45,950 --> 00:19:47,040
Later, a girl came to his house.

425
00:19:51,430 --> 00:19:52,400
After coming to Shangjing,

426
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,400
Yan Bingyun asked others

427
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,640
to call him Mr. Yun.

428
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:56,000
It's said he spent money like water

429
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:57,280
and made a lot of friends.

430
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,680
There were lots of visitors.

431
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:00,560
He just took the opportunity

432
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,680
to collect military information.

433
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:03,520
When he was arrested,

434
00:20:03,520 --> 00:20:05,350
it was some big guys dressed in plain clothes

435
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:06,190
that took him away.

436
00:20:06,430 --> 00:20:07,400
They are secret agents of the Embroidered Uniform Guards.

437
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:09,350
The common people like to watch the scene of bustle most.

438
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:10,920
When he was taken away,

439
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,070
lots of people watched from distance.

440
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:13,520
Nowadays, this issue

441
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:14,760
has become a topic of conversation.

442
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:16,680
Did someone follow them all the way

443
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,560
and happen to find

444
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:18,470
where Yan Bingyun was imprisoned?

445
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:19,520
Of course not.

446
00:20:19,710 --> 00:20:21,160
They're not that curious.

447
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:23,190
Then what's the point of knowing this?

448
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:24,920
It's said that

449
00:20:24,950 --> 00:20:26,190
he's romantic and wealthy.

450
00:20:26,430 --> 00:20:27,920
He also got to know a good girl.

451
00:20:30,230 --> 00:20:31,640
Is that all you found out?

452
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:33,640
What's more,

453
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,520
the same day when he was arrested,

454
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:35,950
that girl came in advance

455
00:20:36,190 --> 00:20:37,590
to ask him to run away.

456
00:20:37,590 --> 00:20:39,190
When those big guys arrived,

457
00:20:39,190 --> 00:20:41,040
she became a weeping beauty

458
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,800
beating and kicking them.

459
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:44,280
But owing to their strength in numbers,

460
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:45,590
Yan Bingyun was taken away, anyway.

461
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,560
Songs and dramas

462
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,070
are full of such stories.

463
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:51,680
It's nobody but Yan Bingyun that was caught.

