472
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,710
Why didn't those guys hit back?

473
00:21:07,430 --> 00:21:08,470
Something is wrong with that girl.

474
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:10,310
Is there any young girl

475
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,310
in the Embroidered Uniform Guards?

476
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:12,400
Definitely not.

477
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,430
Then it's weird.

478
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:16,590
How did that girl know

479
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:18,160
Yan Bingyun would be arrested that day?

480
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,190
Why did those secret agents dare to do nothing to her?

481
00:21:23,830 --> 00:21:26,680
You must've got an answer.

482
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,640
Does Shen Zhong have a daughter?

483
00:21:30,710 --> 00:21:31,350
No.

484
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:32,680
He's not married.

485
00:21:33,470 --> 00:21:35,350
But he has a younger sister.

486
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:37,230
How are they getting along with each other?

487
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:39,350
Their parents died early.

488
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,920
His sister is much younger than him.

489
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:42,520
She was brought up by him.

490
00:21:42,950 --> 00:21:44,310
To his sister,

491
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,880
