and he'll tail after them.

515
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,520
Let them go out?

516
00:22:38,430 --> 00:22:39,230
Exactly.

517
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,950
If there is anyone from the Investigator's Office

518
00:22:41,950 --> 00:22:42,880
who makes contact with Fan Xian,

519
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,190
we can catch the whole lot in an action.

520
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,310
Sounds reasonable.

521
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:49,880
Shall I withdraw them?

522
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,470
Check Wang Qinian out.

523
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:55,190
If it's true,

524
00:22:56,350 --> 00:22:57,760
do as He Daoren said.

525
00:22:59,350 --> 00:23:00,070
Got it.

526
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:18,400
Your Excellency.

527
00:23:22,190 --> 00:23:23,070
Is everything prepared?

528
00:23:23,310 --> 00:23:24,680
Which one do you mean?

529
00:23:25,350 --> 00:23:26,830
All messages about Beiqi

530
00:23:27,430 --> 00:23:28,590
sent by Yan Bingyun

531
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:30,070
before he was arrested.

532
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:31,350
Head Chen wants to present them

533
00:23:31,350 --> 00:23:32,160
to His Majesty.

534
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:33,040
The sooner the better.

535
00:23:33,040 --> 00:23:33,800
Got it.

536
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:38,830
Your Excellency, it's prepared.

537
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,040
