554
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:38,520
Fan Xian find Yan Bingyun.

555
00:25:05,280 --> 00:25:07,070
That is Shen Zhong's younger sister.

556
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,710
What will you do?

557
00:25:10,110 --> 00:25:10,800
Kidnap her?

558
00:25:12,760 --> 00:25:13,640
That's extreme.

559
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:41,590
Won't you follow her?

560
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,950
Wang Qinian is better at lightness skill.

561
00:26:35,470 --> 00:26:36,310
Your Excellency,

562
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:38,880
